OL,3,CRebuild begins after gas explosion
OL,4,Cdestroyed four homes
OL,6,FWork has begun to replace four
OL,7,Fproperties badly damaged in an
OL,8,Fexplosion three years ago.
OL,10,FSeven people were injured, two with
OL,11,Flife-changing injuries, after the
OL,12,Fblast ripped through homes in Ashford,
OL,13,FKent on 4 May 2021.
OL,15,FThe explosion was caused by a leak
OL,16,Ffrom a portable gas heater in one of
OL,17,Fthe homes at Mill View terrace in
OL,18,FWillesborough.
