OL,3,CRebuild begins after gas explosion
OL,4,Cdestroyed four homes
OL,6,FThree council-owned properties and one
OL,7,Fprivately owned home were badly
OL,8,Fdamaged, and alternative accommodation
OL,9,Fwas provided for the people affected.
OL,11,FAshford Borough Council has started
OL,12,Fthe work, which is expected to be
OL,13,Fcompleted by August 2025.
OL,15,FThe new homes will be built with a
OL,16,Ffocus on energy efficiency, including
OL,17,Fsolar panels on roofs.
